author: Gabriel Elizondo
title: Empty streets are new normal in New York
description: The shutdown of New York has turned one of the most vibrant cities in the world into a ghost town.
content: New York Governor Andrew Cuomo announced last week, April 17, that the shutdown of New York would continue until at least May 15. New York City, the epicentre of the coronavirus outbreak with more than 100,000 cases and nine thousand deaths (as of April 17), … [+214 chars]
